  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nFollow up from https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/15594\r\nThe issue is still reproducible, but not in 100% of cases. \r\n\r\nSteps to reproduce:\r\n1. Record and send an audio message\r\n2. Start playing audio, pause it\r\n3. Send the app to the background\r\n4. Open the app\r\n5. Tap play\r\n\r\nHere is an example of when it reproduces:\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/236413553-43d87383-604c-41c0-9da8-a0542f27334e.mp4\r\n\r\nAnd here is when it works fine:\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/236413603-cb755520-c928-435c-a741-bf92e6bb0b74.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly 5/05\r\n- Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
